[It appears now that vaccine doses also will be sent. It is critical that countries that have the resources available share those with less developed countries. If we can't achieve equity in vaccination, the outbreak will continue to surge in countries without vaccines available and consequently extremely low vaccination rates. There is unacceptable inequity not only among different groups of people in each country, but also between countries. The existing inequities are being exacerbated by COVID-19. - Mod.LK]

